# @krxon/krx

AUTO-GENERATED by `krxon` from KRX Open API spec.

## Install

```bash
npm install @krxon/krx
```

## Usage

```ts
import { KrxClient } from "@krxon/krx";

const client = new KrxClient();
const data = await client.getKrxIndexDaily({ basDd: "20260313" });
console.log(data[0]);
```

